Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(197.4,200.557)}{\fs25\c&H78BDE7&\fad(0,808)}24小时\N\N{\fs15}第三季  第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫医生 救人!\N{\r原文字幕}We need medical assistance. Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是保安 坡道口需要增援\N{\r原文字幕}This is security, I need help here at the ramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官们 监狱主区一级防范禁闭中\N{\r原文字幕}Officers, main blocks are in lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备...\N{\r原文字幕}Stand by...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以进了 长官\N{\r原文字幕}Go, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把右手放到扫描屏上\N{\r原文字幕}Right hand on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,验证通过\N{\r原文字幕}It's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请过来拿回你们的身份证明\N{\r原文字幕}Step over there please. I'll give back your IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开1号门\N{\r原文字幕}Open 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 杰克?\N{\r原文字幕}You're ok, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,协议签了 我就会好了\N{\r原文字幕}I'll feel ok until we get this thing signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指那个\N{\r原文字幕}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人都到齐了\N{\r原文字幕}Ok, we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有什么变动?  -别紧张 杰克 没有大变动\N{\r原文字幕}-What kind of change is we're talking about?  -Don't worry, Jack. They're not deal breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是得供出一部分恐怖组织名单\N{\r原文字幕}He's still gonna give a part of terrorist cells he deals with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他想接受二级监禁 而不是最高监禁\N{\r原文字幕}He just want to go to a classe 2 detention. Not maximum security.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你们会满足他的要求吧?  -会的\N{\r原文字幕}-And you're gonna give it to him, right?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当事人要被带离弗罗里达州 他很不满\N{\r原文字幕}My client's not happy that you won't hold him in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-协议规定他得去明尼苏达州  -让他留在弗罗里达 一样的\N{\r原文字幕}-He's getting Minnesota, that's the deal.  -Give him Florida, it doesn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管到我头上来了好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}I let you two do your jobs, why won't let you do mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想为了些小事 把问题转移到南部\N{\r原文字幕}Because we don't want this thing going South over small detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉扎捉摸不透 不知什么时候又会惹麻烦\N{\r原文字幕}Salazar is instable, we can't predict what's gonna push his buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-实话说: 事情很棘手  -听着 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}-and to be frank: there's too much in stake.  -Listen Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你俩用了一年时间才抓到萨拉扎 我深表敬佩\N{\r原文字幕}I know you two spend last year getting Salazar and I respect that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但我得按章办事...  -路易斯 过来一下\N{\r原文字幕}-but there's a protocol that I have to follow...  -Luis, come here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重点不是要看管好他\N{\r原文字幕}Putting him away, it's not the point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不开口 我们就白忙活了\N{\r原文字幕}If he doesn't talk, we haven't accomplished anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了一年时间 可不仅仅是为了抓个毒贩\N{\r原文字幕}I didn't lose a year of my life to arrest some drug dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉扎和全球范围的恐怖组织做过交易\N{\r原文字幕}Salazar does business with terrorist cells around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拿下他们是我们唯一的目标 懂吗?  -我懂\N{\r原文字幕}-Bringing them down is our only objective, are we clear?  -I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你什么都依着他 他会更加得寸进尺\N{\r原文字幕}But if you give Salazar everything he asked for, he's just gonna want more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是协议 他必须服从\N{\r原文字幕}This is the deal and he's going to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你别做错事\N{\r原文字幕}You'd better be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在任由你们宰割?\N{\r原文字幕}Is that my life you're holding in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以签了\N{\r原文字幕}It's ready to be signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那儿吗 杰克?\N{\r原文字幕}Are you in there, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了他吧\N{\r原文字幕}Forget about Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么忘得了那个抓我进来的人? 假装朋友接近我?\N{\r原文字幕}How can I forget about the man who put me here? Pretended to be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你哦 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}I'm concerned about you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了抓我 你做的那些事...\N{\r原文字幕}The things you did to get me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟别人说\N{\r原文字幕}I wouldn't wish on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对现实吧 你已不是原来的你\N{\r原文字幕}Let's face it, you'll never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈! 我也一样\N{\r原文字幕}Hey! Neither will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩在一条船上\N{\r原文字幕}So, I guess we are in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公开说吧 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}I'm about to name names, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天对我俩都会意义重大\N{\r原文字幕}This is a big moment for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太高兴了\N{\r原文字幕}That makes me happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们被联系起来了\N{\r原文字幕}because you see, we are connected now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这是注定的?\N{\r原文字幕}I don't know, maybe we always have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我把有变动的地方做了标注  -我不需要看\N{\r原文字幕}-I've marked the changes.  -I don't need to see the changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只需要一只钢笔\N{\r原文字幕}but I do need a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你要我蘸自己的血签字\N{\r原文字幕}Unless you want me to sign it with my own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 我自己的血\N{\r原文字幕}It's kind of funny. My own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿签?\N{\r原文字幕}Where do I sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里\N{\r原文字幕}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为我的法律顾问 你干得不错\N{\r原文字幕}You've done a good job as my counsellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但正式地说 还差最后一步\N{\r原文字幕}In a go to guy, as they like to say here in States.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你坦白过很多事\N{\r原文字幕}I think that I own to you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你得闭上嘴才算尽了职  -什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}-but I don't think you have what it takes to keep your mouth shut.  -What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗杂种!\N{\r原文字幕}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门! 开门!\N{\r原文字幕}Open the door! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点! 快!\N{\r原文字幕}Do it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫医生!\N{\r原文字幕}Get a medic in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是你的错 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}This is your fault, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-接下来就轮到你了  -你想威胁?\N{\r原文字幕}-And what happens next is on you too.  -Is that a threat? Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-狗杂种!  -退后! 你先出去!\N{\r原文字幕}-Son of a bitch!  -Back off! Take a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就轮到你了 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}What happens next is on you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你了!\N{\r原文字幕}It's on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马切尔医生? 我们照你吩咐隔离了尸体\N{\r原文字幕}Dr. Macer? We isolated the body like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你说上面有我的名字?  -是 在尸体胸口\N{\r原文字幕}-You said my name was on it?  -Yes, it's on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做个全面检查以防万一\N{\r原文字幕}Spread a full panel of tests just to be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我想我们遇到了新型3号类型免疫病毒  -3号类型?\N{\r原文字幕}-but I think we're dealing with a new immuno-virus type 3.  -Type 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不正是你们小组正在研究的类型吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Isn't that the virus group your team's been doing simulations on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 所以才把这个寄给我吧\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, I think that's why this was addressed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知反恐局了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Has CTU been contacted again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没 我们在等你\N{\r原文字幕}No, we're been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你去做初步检测 我去通知指挥官阿尔梅达  -好的\N{\r原文字幕}-Go ahead and start the preliminary tests, I'll call Director Almeida.  -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 总统到SC了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Hey! the President arrived at SC yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚到 我们正在安排人手 情报局的已经就绪了\N{\r原文字幕}Just about. We're swapping at some of our people now and the secret service is in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们在等你的评估报告  -好 我打给他\N{\r原文字幕}-They're waiting for your resource assessment.  -Alright, I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-托尼 上帝知道我受够了!  -怎么了 亚当?\N{\r原文字幕}-I've had it Tony, I swear to God!  -What's the problem, Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萝伊·奥布莱恩没使用我的数据\N{\r原文字幕}Chloe O'Brian does not touch my data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果外勤组有什么需要 她去问杰克或你 你再告诉我\N{\r原文字幕}If field ops wants something, she asks Jack or talks to you, and you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她惹麻烦了吗?  -问题不在这儿\N{\r原文字幕}-Did she damage anything?  -That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我部门之所以做到零故障 是因为我将一切规程做得井然有序\N{\r原文字幕}The reason my department has zero down time is because of the procedures I put in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她惹麻烦了吗?  -没有但我...  -行了\N{\r原文字幕}-Did she damage anything?  -No, she didn't but I will...  -Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克管他的部门 我管我的 大家都在同一屋檐下工作 懂吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Look, Jack's got his department, I got mine. We are all in the same roof, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\r原文字幕}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松点\N{\r原文字幕}Now lighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把自己和别人逼疯了\N{\r原文字幕}Don't drive yourself and the rest of us crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 请稍等\N{\r原文字幕}All right, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫生部索尼·马切尔医生的电话 还有 有赫尔佐格的消息吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Sony Macer from Health services is on the line. By the way, have you heard from Hertzog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有\N{\r原文字幕}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松 米歇尔 你会得到那份工作\N{\r原文字幕}Relax, Michelle, you're gonna get the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是 没有我 你不能去找兰利\N{\r原文字幕}It had better, you're not going in Langley without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 桑尼 什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}Hey! Sunny, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-很抱歉是坏消息  -什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}-This is what I'm really sorry to be right about.  -What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科迪利亚病毒 3号类型的免疫病毒 记得上月的会议吗\N{\r原文字幕}Cordella virus, it's a type 3 immuno-virus. Remember last month at the conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提出病毒可能会被培育出来\N{\r原文字幕}I raised the possibility a strain could be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯  -说中了\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah.  -Well, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人扔下了一具感染了病毒的尸体\N{\r原文字幕}Someone just dropped out a dead body infected with a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 这些人是玩真格的 他们在引起我们的注意\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, these guys are serious. They blew a hole in the door to get our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这显然是个警告  -警告?\N{\r原文字幕}-This is obviously some kind of message.  -A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有人携有病毒并要传播病毒?  -正是\N{\r原文字幕}-What? That somebody's got the virus and is willing to release it?  -Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们需要签发疫情公告吗?  -不 一旦宿主死了 就不再有传染性\N{\r原文字幕}-Do we need to issue a quarantine adviser?  -No, once the host is dead, he's not contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮个忙 查一下地方部门有没有发现类似案例\N{\r原文字幕}Right, do me a favour, call the other county facilities and see if there's anymore cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 怎么查死者身份?\N{\r原文字幕}I will. What about the ID on the John Doe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你那的所有线索送过来 我们来查\N{\r原文字幕}Send everything you have over here. We'll work it up.
