Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪活动? 就凭一具死尸?\N{\r原文字幕}Criminal action? Based on this one death?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.70,0:31:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚细节 大卫 这和尸体被发现的环境有关\N{\r原文字幕}I don't know the details David but it has to do with the circumstances in which the body was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.10,0:31:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-留意此事  -好的\N{\r原文字幕}-Keep your eye on this one.  -Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.40,0:31:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-恰克 开始关于国土安全的第7个问题  -好的\N{\r原文字幕}-Chuck, can we go on the question number 7 please about homeland security?  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.00,0:31:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-在?  -萨拉扎和检察官的记录呢?\N{\r原文字幕}-Yes?  -Where is the transcript of Salazar and the D.A.?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.00,0:31:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发到你电脑里了 在你的文件目录中\N{\r原文字幕}I sent them to your system, it's in your directory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 我不想存在目录里 我希望它和其它萨拉扎资料放在一起!\N{\r原文字幕}Damn it, I didn't want it in my directory, I wanted it stored with the rest of the files from Salazar!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.80,0:31:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我照办\N{\r原文字幕}Ok, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.70,0:31:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萝伊 要是你不能一次性把事情办好 我就换一个能做好的\N{\r原文字幕}Chloe, listen to me. If you can't start getting things right the first time, just let me know because I can get someone else who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.40,0:31:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做好 如果你想把它和其他文件放一起 你就该事先告诉我\N{\r原文字幕}I did do it right. If you wanted it with the other files, you should have said so that it isn't standard so I wouldn't think of doing it in that way, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.90,0:31:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在起照我的方式做! 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Just do it that way from now on! Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.60,0:31:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会读心术 杰克 有要求你得说明白\N{\r原文字幕}I can't read minds, Jack, you've just gonna have to spell it out for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.00,0:31:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则我们的工作关系...\N{\r原文字幕}otherwise this relationship won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.00,0:31:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 克萝伊! 快去干活!\N{\r原文字幕}Damn it, Chloe! Just do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.80,0:31:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\r原文字幕}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.40,0:32:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 杰克  -干嘛?\N{\r原文字幕}-Hey Jack.  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.10,0:32:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-刚才怎么了?  -帮我换掉克萝伊\N{\r原文字幕}-What was that about?  -I need you to replace Chloe for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.20,0:32:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-换掉? 但她是最棒的分析师  -她哪有 她太慢\N{\r原文字幕}-Replace her? But she's the best analyst we got.  -No, she's not. She's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.20,0:32:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不慢 她有些古怪 但精通业务\N{\r原文字幕}She's not slow. I mean, she may be a little weird but she knows her stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.60,0:32:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你状态很糟\N{\r原文字幕}You look like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.70,0:32:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What did you say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们处在警备状态? 不知你是否会失控\N{\r原文字幕}Well, we're in actif protocol, ok? And I need to know if you're up for it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.00,0:32:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯 我喜欢你 你是个不错的孩子\N{\r原文字幕}I like you Chase, you're a nice kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:32:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不许到我办公室那样对我说话 懂吗?\N{\r原文字幕}But don't you ever come in my office and talk to me like that again. Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.40,0:33:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说你情绪焦燥\N{\r原文字幕}I'm just saying you're on edge. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.40,0:33:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是在无故开除克萝伊\N{\r原文字幕}I mean, come on man, you're about to fire Chloe for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萝伊 抱歉刚才对你发火 我只是情绪不好\N{\r原文字幕}Chloe, I'm sorry I took your head off. I was just in a bad mood. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.60,0:33:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你满意了?\N{\r原文字幕}You're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.10,0:33:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 我还有件事要告诉你\N{\r原文字幕}Look Jack, there's one more thing I've gotta talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.20,0:33:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我们马上下来\N{\r原文字幕}Ok, we'll be right down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.40,0:33:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉扎有情况\N{\r原文字幕}They got something on Salazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.40,0:33:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想告诉我什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you wanna tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.60,0:33:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 以后再谈\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing. It will hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.40,0:33:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\r原文字幕}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.10,0:34:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了防范安全疏漏 现在起我们每天进行检查\N{\r原文字幕}So, in order to plug any possible security breaches, we're doing day checks from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.20,0:34:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最长8小时做一次工作记录...\N{\r原文字幕}Break your logs into 8 hours or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没 现在太忙 但我保证会说的\N{\r原文字幕}No, there's a lot going on right now. It will happen, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.00,0:34:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟前有人给FBI打了匿名电话\N{\r原文字幕}An anonymous phone call just came in FBI by 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.30,0:34:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都来听听\N{\r原文字幕}We're getting into this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.30,0:34:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你听过吗?  -嗯\N{\r原文字幕}-Did you hear it?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.40,0:34:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-准备就绪  -播录音\N{\r原文字幕}-Ok, it's ready.  -Bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们收到了我们寄的东西 并知道我们拥有3号型肺部病毒\N{\r原文字幕}I know you received our package and realize we're in possession of a type 3 pulmonary immuno-virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.80,0:34:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听着 我们的要求很简单\N{\r原文字幕}Listen very carefully to these instructions. Our demand is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.00,0:34:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6小时内释放拉姆·萨拉扎\N{\r原文字幕}We want the release of Ram Salazar in the next 6 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.60,0:34:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒绝 病毒就会散播到人群中\N{\r原文字幕}If you refuse to comply, the virus will be unleashed to the general population.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你们专家说的一样 你们没时间阻止病毒的传播\N{\r原文字幕}As your experts will tell you, you would not have time to stop its spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.90,0:35:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍后再通知你们交人的细节\N{\r原文字幕}Details how Ram is to be delivering will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就这些  -知道电话来源吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-That's it.  -Do we know where the phone call originated from?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.00,0:35:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 信号从卫星转来\N{\r原文字幕}We don't know yet. It came from a scrambled satellites,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.50,0:35:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在缩小范围\N{\r原文字幕}you know. We're trying to narrow it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.10,0:35:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 你最了解萨拉扎 你估计此人是谁\N{\r原文字幕}Jack, you know Salazar better than anybody else here. Who do you think we're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.10,0:35:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是他兄弟 二把手赫克托\N{\r原文字幕}Without a doubt his brother. Hector was next in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.10,0:35:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆被收押后 他迅速躲了起来\N{\r原文字幕}He went underground the second Ram was taken into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.10,0:35:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道萨拉扎在南美和墨西哥有大量财产\N{\r原文字幕}Now look, I know for a fact that the Salazars own multiple properties in South America and Mexico
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚设公司 注册了资金\N{\r原文字幕}registered under dummy corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.50,0:35:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 现在墨西哥政府也找不到他们\N{\r原文字幕}Unfortunately, right now, the Mexican government, it seems they can't locate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.40,0:35:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只能撒大网 追踪电话来源\N{\r原文字幕}So we've gonna to throw out a pretty large net to try and trace the origin of that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.70,0:35:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们会努力的  -对了 死者身份查到了吗\N{\r原文字幕}-Right, we'll work on it.  -Ok. How are we doing with the ID on the dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.80,0:35:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-米歇尔正在分析DNA  -指纹和牙齿呢?\N{\r原文字幕}-Michelle is working on the DNA.  -Ok. What about prints and dental?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.10,0:35:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没牙齿 没指尖\N{\r原文字幕}No teeth, no finger tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.10,0:35:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须找出死者身份 这是追查对方活动的唯一线索了\N{\r原文字幕}Ok. Look, we need this ID. This's the only hook we've got into their operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-萨拉扎审得如何?  -完全是浪费时间 他很强悍\N{\r原文字幕}-What about questionning Salazar?  -Complete waste of time. This is a man without vulnerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用刑对他不起作用\N{\r原文字幕}He doesn't respond to physical interrogation,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.20,0:35:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也不在乎别人的死活 包括他的子女\N{\r原文字幕}and he doesn't care about another living soul including his own children.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.60,0:35:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 发现一个符合死者的身份\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, we've a match on John Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.60,0:36:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 有何发现?\N{\r原文字幕}Michelle, what did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.00,0:36:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者叫大卫·戈斯 洛杉矶东部的街头毒贩 也卖些小道消息\N{\r原文字幕}The dead body is a David Goss. He's a street dealer in east L.A., also an informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.70,0:36:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来他逃脱了几次 禁药局也一年多没管他了\N{\r原文字幕}It looks like he flips sides some many times DEA stopped working for over more a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.40,0:36:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-知道他最后去过哪儿吗?  -我们正在查\N{\r原文字幕}-Do we have a last known address?  -We're working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要弄清谁让戈斯感染病毒\N{\r原文字幕}Ok. We're gonna need to know who infected Goss.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.70,0:36:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出最后几周和他接触过之人的名单\N{\r原文字幕}You've gonna to work up a list of everyone who's being involved in this life over the last weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们齐心协力从这儿入手查案\N{\r原文字幕}All right. We'll pull together everything we got hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.60,0:36:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 同时也要从萨拉扎的毒品网络入手\N{\r原文字幕}Ok, but work it from the other side as well, go through Salazar network.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.60,0:36:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看是否能找到戈斯的毒品供应者 好好干\N{\r原文字幕}See if you can find this supplier who sold to Goss. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.60,0:36:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来 蔡斯 看能不能从赫克托这发现什么\N{\r原文字幕}Chase, come with me. We'll see if anything is coming on Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.40,0:38:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让我爸帮你干这活儿? 这不是他的工作\N{\r原文字幕}Why do have my father doing this kind of work for you? It's not his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.60,0:38:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就今天\N{\r原文字幕}It is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.60,0:38:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要杀沙耶?\N{\r原文字幕}Why did you kill Shaye?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.10,0:38:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看周围 拉姆\N{\r原文字幕}Take a look around, Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.80,0:38:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是美国监狱 还没上法场你的屁股就会坐烂\N{\r原文字幕}You're in an U.S. prison where your ass is going to rot until you're executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.40,0:38:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想改善条件吗? 那就老实交待\N{\r原文字幕}You want to improve your condition here? You'd better start talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.20,0:38:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-交待什么?  -为什么要杀你的律师?\N{\r原文字幕}-What do you want to talk about?  -Why did you kill your attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.65,0:38:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让他告诉你们\N{\r原文字幕}I didn't want him talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.65,0:38:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉什么?  -所有一切\N{\r原文字幕}-About what?  -About anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.80,0:39:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很不爽?\N{\r原文字幕}It's eating at you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你还等什么\N{\r原文字幕}What am I up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.70,0:39:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧路易斯 我被拷着 这俩看守马上可以把我打得满地找牙\N{\r原文字幕}Come on, Luis. You have me in chains. Two tough guys waiting for a chance to beat me to a pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.10,0:39:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 路易斯! 看看用刑能不能逼我开口!\N{\r原文字幕}Do it, Luis! See if you can me beat it out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好玩儿\N{\r原文字幕}You are no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.80,0:39:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿?\N{\r原文字幕}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.40,0:40:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?\N{\r原文字幕}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.40,0:40:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲是个农场工头\N{\r原文字幕}My father is a ranch foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.50,0:40:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过不让他卷入你的那些勾当\N{\r原文字幕}You promised me he wouldn't be involved in your other activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.60,0:40:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我付给你父亲三倍薪酬\N{\r原文字幕}I pay your father 3 times more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.90,0:40:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 我答应到这住 但条件是不让父亲和弟弟 沾上你那不干净的生意\N{\r原文字幕}No! I told you when we came to live here that I didn't want him or my little brother to be exposed to your illegal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.00,0:40:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你食言了 赫克托\N{\r原文字幕}You broke your word, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.20,0:40:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你伤害了我\N{\r原文字幕}And that hurts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.60,0:40:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难过\N{\r原文字幕}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.60,0:40:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对不起 克劳迪娅 我会补偿你的  -怎样补偿?\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm sorry Claudia, please I'll make it up to you.  -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让你爸休假 再多付一个月资金\N{\r原文字幕}I'll give your father some time off, an extra month pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.20,0:40:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你解决问题的方式? 用钱...\N{\r原文字幕}That's your solution to every problem, isn't it? Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.60,0:41:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-给FBI打过电话了吗?  -打过了\N{\r原文字幕}-Have you made the call to the FBI?  -Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.10,0:41:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 我们的猎物呢?\N{\r原文字幕}And... what about our boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.10,0:41:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我在监视他  -仔细监视\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm watching him now.  -Keep him close.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\r原文字幕}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.50,0:41:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在提华纳做事是什么感觉?\N{\r原文字幕}So, what was it like to get knee deep in some fine Tijuana tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.90,0:41:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我在那儿做事  -什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}-I did not do that.  -What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.90,0:41:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有去那儿 我被解雇了\N{\r原文字幕}I mean I didn't go down there to get laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.60,0:41:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但你说...  -是的... 我说过\N{\r原文字幕}-But you said...  -I know... I know what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.20,0:41:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一 有些事我没告诉你\N{\r原文字幕}I just didn't wanna tell you in case something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.00,0:42:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么秘密?\N{\r原文字幕}What's the big secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.50,0:42:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-记得高中同学扎克·帕克吗?  -嗯\N{\r原文字幕}-You remember Zach Parker from High school?  -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.30,0:42:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年他不是因为贩毒被学校开除了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Didn't he get busted last year for dealing coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 他设计让我认识那男人\N{\r原文字幕}Whatever, he set me up to this guy from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-设计? 你怎么认识他的?  -我就是认识他! 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-What do you mean he set you up? How do you even know him?  -I know him! Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都干什么了老兄? 卖麻药?\N{\r原文字幕}What are you into here man? You're selling dope?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.10,0:42:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准确说不是...\N{\r原文字幕}No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.30,0:42:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准确说你干嘛了?\N{\r原文字幕}So exactly what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.50,0:42:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人付了我五千美元 帮他把毒品带入境 就在昨天\N{\r原文字幕}This guy, he payed me $5000 to bring some coke over the border. I did that last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.90,0:42:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我把毒品送过去 又挣了五千美元\N{\r原文字幕}Today, I drop it off. I get another $5000.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你疯了吧  -就一次\N{\r原文字幕}-You goota be out of your mind.  -This is one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.50,0:42:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-过境可不容易 但还是做到了  -你为什么这么做?\N{\r原文字幕}-Getting over the border was the hard part. It's already done.  -Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.20,0:42:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈要做透析 我爸失业了\N{\r原文字幕}My mum is under dialysis, my dad is out of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.20,0:42:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要被房东赶出这鬼地方\N{\r原文字幕}We're about to get evicted from this crappy appartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.10,0:43:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-懂了吗?  -你彻底疯了\N{\r原文字幕}-Is that good enough for you?  -You are seriously insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.10,0:43:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆 今天我还会去干一笔\N{\r原文字幕}Look Tim, I'm about to make this drop later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.90,0:43:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我想... 也许我们可以一起干...  -不行! 休想!\N{\r原文字幕}-I was just thinking maybe... maybe you and I, we could go together...  -Forget it! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.20,0:43:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在车里等 我去送毒品 再回来 就这么简单\N{\r原文字幕}You wait in the car. I go in, I make the drop, I come back, and that's it. There's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.20,0:43:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不感兴趣\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.00,0:43:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑一下嘛\N{\r原文字幕}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.00,0:43:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-FBI什么时候接到的电话  -20分钟前\N{\r原文字幕}-When did FBI get this call?  -About 20 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.00,0:43:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道谁打来的?\N{\r原文字幕}And we don't know who we're dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.80,0:43:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来电声音经过了处理 电话只说\N{\r原文字幕}It was a scrambled voice on an open line. All we know is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不交出萨拉扎 就散播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}They want Salazar or they're gonna release the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.80,0:43:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想 韦恩? 取消辩论?\N{\r原文字幕}What's your take on this, Wayne? Do we cancel the debate?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前 国防部和反恐局建议提高警戒级别...\N{\r原文字幕}So far, DOD, the Pentagone and CTU have recommended raising the alert level but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.00,0:44:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在商量我们是否该继续留在洛杉矶\N{\r原文字幕}they are discussing whether or not we should stay in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.00,0:44:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-总统阁下  -什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-Sir.  -Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.70,0:44:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕卡德医生来了 她想见你\N{\r原文字幕}Doctor Packard is here, she's asked to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.90,0:44:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉她我很忙  -是 阁下\N{\r原文字幕}-Tell her I'm busy please.  -Yes, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.40,0:44:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦 等等 带她来见我\N{\r原文字幕}Aaron, wait. Tell her I'll speak with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.80,0:44:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要去见她?\N{\r原文字幕}You really wanna do that right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.70,0:44:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 韦恩\N{\r原文字幕}Yes, Wayne, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.60,0:44:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 安妮\N{\r原文字幕}Yes, Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.20,0:44:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃这个药 早晚各一片\N{\r原文字幕}I want you to start taking these. One on the morning and one before you go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.50,0:44:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你恢复精力\N{\r原文字幕}It will help your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.60,0:44:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我没事\N{\r原文字幕}I told you I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.80,0:44:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说过 你不相信医生了?\N{\r原文字幕}I know what you told me. Are you gonna trust your doctor or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.20,0:45:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信\N{\r原文字幕}Of course, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.50,0:45:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 你看起来很烦恼\N{\r原文字幕}What's going on? You seem upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 这段时间天天都这样...\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing. It's just gonna be another one of those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.20,0:45:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.60,0:45:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得过去工作了\N{\r原文字幕}I've got to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧  -下次聊\N{\r原文字幕}-Ok.  -We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.90,0:45:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这系统怎么了?  -什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-What is wrong with this system?  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.80,0:45:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网格无法显示\N{\r原文字幕}The grid won't come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.60,0:45:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个控制通路\N{\r原文字幕}Because you need a control access.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.80,0:46:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在导航界面\N{\r原文字幕}You're still on navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.60,0:46:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\r原文字幕}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.80,0:46:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它传到我办公室好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Look, can you just patch it through to my office?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.80,0:46:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他今天怎么了?  -没事\N{\r原文字幕}-What's his problem today?  -Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.80,0:46:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时间表没用 记录从12月直到2月\N{\r原文字幕}This timeline does not make a sense, it goes straight from December to February.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.90,0:46:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛 杰克?\N{\r原文字幕}What are you trying to do, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.90,0:46:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解决问题 你也该试试\N{\r原文字幕}Same thing you should be trying to do. Solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.60,0:46:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指这个\N{\r原文字幕}That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.60,0:46:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Listen Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.20,0:46:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实对你说\N{\r原文字幕}I'm gonna be honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.00,0:46:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尊敬你\N{\r原文字幕}I look up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.20,0:46:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要我愿意为你而死 但现在坦白说\N{\r原文字幕}I'd take a bullet for you if I had to but right now I'm gonna hold the mirror up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.40,0:46:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接近萨拉扎有6个月\N{\r原文字幕}You were under of Salazar for 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.90,0:47:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们对你做了什么\N{\r原文字幕}I know what they did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.40,0:47:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你对自己做了什么\N{\r原文字幕}And I know what you did to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.80,0:47:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无法短时间摆脱那些事\N{\r原文字幕}You can't make that go away over night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.00,0:47:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我不知道吗?\N{\r原文字幕}You think I didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.60,0:47:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不关你的事 蔡斯\N{\r原文字幕}You should mind you own business, Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.90,0:47:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你\N{\r原文字幕}All I'm trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.50,0:47:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来是为你工作\N{\r原文字幕}is that I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.60,0:47:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但今天不是你向大家证明你更强大的日子\N{\r原文字幕}But today is not the day to try to prove to everybody that you are better.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.60,0:47:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会对你产生不利影响 你我都清楚\N{\r原文字幕}It's about to hit hard, you know that and I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.60,0:47:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做回以前的自己吧\N{\r原文字幕}So do what you've gotta do, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.50,0:47:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调整好自己 我们才能展开工作\N{\r原文字幕}Get your head straight, so we can do our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.60,0:49:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 你在上面吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad, you're up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.40,0:50:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.80,0:50:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.40,0:50:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能上来吗? 我有事要告诉你\N{\r原文字幕}Can I come up? I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.60,0:50:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行 孩子 我正在处理东西\N{\r原文字幕}Not right now, sweetheart, I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.00,0:50:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 有空打给我\N{\r原文字幕}Ok, well call me when you have a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.50,0:50:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\r原文字幕}Ok.
